requirement: 5.1/H-1-1: Advertise the maximum number of hardware video decoder sessions that can be run concurrently in any codec combination
5.1/H-1-2: Support 6 instances of hardware video decoder sessions (AVC, VP8, HEVC, VP9 or later) in any codec combination running concurrently at 720p resolution@30fps.
5.1/H-1-5: Advertise the maximum number of hardware video encoder and decoder sessions that can be run concurrently in any codec combination
